name: In Death God Loves You
description:
Death, who is not afraid of death? Death is the biggest fear by some people. Everyone wants to delay their deaths. Long live and glorious hahahaha. Are you sure that longevity will be more useful? With a long life, what are you doing to do?. 
Surrender to death. Death is not the end point. Where there is an existance, there will be change. Death is not the end of you, it is simply the process of energy change and interconnectedity with the universe. In the process God loves you in the form of more beneficial energy changes.
